4. **Policy** — NIST SP 800-207 / 800-207A Zero Trust controls (ZT-1…ZT-8), 
   HIPAA/SOC2/PCI overlays, evidence + one-click remediation
5. **IaC** — Export to Pulumi/Terraform/Helm/CloudFormation; import from live 
   cloud + Terraform state with drift detection

