- Cost model: catalog baseline × HA factor (1.0/1.6/2.4/3.0) × scaling units
- Agent pipeline: LLM narrative + **deterministic planner** as structured tool 
  (templates: three-tier, serverless; talk-to-edit via regex mutations)
